<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">

    <!-- CSS -->
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.1.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet"
        integrity="sha384-1BmE4kWBq78iYhFldvKuhfTAU6auU8tT94WrHftjDbrCEXSU1oBoqyl2QvZ6jIW3" crossorigin="anonymous">

    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/static/css/navbar/area.css">

    <title>Solar Zone</title>
</head>

<body>

    <section class="main">
        <h1>How do I calculate a solar panel’s output ?</h1>
        <div class="info">
            <ul>
                <li>Most residential solar panels on today’s market are rated to produce between 250 and 400 watts each
                    per hour.</li>
                <li>Domestic solar panel systems typically have a capacity of between 1 kW and 4 kW.</li>
                <li>A 4 kW solar panel system on an average-sized house in Yorkshire can produce around 2,850 kWh of
                    electricity in a year.</li>
                <li> Most Solar Panel are between 15% and 20% efficient.</li>
                <li>A solar panel’s output depends on several factors, including its size, capacity, your location, and
                    weather conditions.</li>
            </ul>
        </div>
        <h3>Work out how much electricity—measured in kilowatt hours (kWh).</h3>
        <div class="info">
            <ul>
                <li>Assume Solar Panel is 20% efficient.</li>
                <li>All Unit is kilowatt format.</li>
            </ul>
        </div>
        <h3>Solar panel output per day :</h3>
        <div class="input-box">
            <div class="input">
                <label for="size">Enter the Solar panels size <br>(square kilometres) :</label>
                <input type="number" id="size">
            </div>
            <div class="input">
                <label for="light">Enter the Your area gets sun <br> per day(hr) :</label>
                <input type="number" id="light">
            </div>
            <button type="button" id="btn" class="btn btn-outline-primary">Apply</button>
            <div class="result">
                <h4 class="heading" id="heading"></h4>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>


    <!-- JavaScript -->

    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.1.3/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"
        integrity="sha384-ka7Sk0Gln4gmtz2MlQnikT1wXgYsOg+OMhuP+IlRH9sENBO0LRn5q+8nbTov4+1p"
        crossorigin="anonymous"></script>

    <script src="/static/js/area.js"></script>

</body>

</html>